name: Fryer Process Data Dump
query:
Declare @date datetime=getdate()
Declare @fromdate datetime
Declare @todate datetime

If DATEPART(hour,@date) between 6 and 23
begin
Set @fromdate=concat(convert(date,@date),' 06:00:00.000')
Set @todate=concat(convert(date,@date),' 23:59:59')
end
if DATEPART(hour,@date) between 0 and 5
begin
Set @fromdate=concat(dateadd(day,-1,convert(date,@date)),' 06:00:00.000')
Set @todate=concat(convert(date,@date),' 05:59:59')
end

SELECT *  FROM [ITC_PANCHLA_DB].[dbo].[PC_FRYER_PROCESS] where DateAndTime between @fromdate and @todate
order by DateAndTime

var tempData = []

const months = [
    "Jan",
    "Feb",
    "Mar",
    "Apr",
    "May",
    "Jun",
    "Jul",
    "Aug",
    "Sep",
    "Oct",
    "Nov",
    "Dec"
]

for (i = 0; i < months.length; i++) {
    const dataSet = {
        "temp" : Math.random() * 30,
        "month" : months[i]
    }
    tempData.push(dataSet)
}

msg.payload = tempData

return msg;

<style id="hotNipi-gauge">
:root{
    --needle-color:#001100;
    --needle-second-color:#ff0000;
    --red-ticks:9;
    --sec-high-color:#ff00004f;
    --sec-normal-color:#00ff004f;

}
.g-container {
    padding-top: 3px;
    padding-bottom: 3px;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    user-select:none;
}
    
.g-body {
    width: 98%;
    height: 98%;
    border-radius: 15%;
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    box-shadow: 0px 5px 8px #00000045;
    background: linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(78,78,78,1) 0%, rgba(215,215,215,1) 99%, rgba(236,236,236,1) 100%);
}

.g-body::before {    
    content: "";
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0naHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmcnIHdpZHRoPSc1JyBoZWlnaHQ9JzUnPgogIDxyZWN0IHdpZHRoPSc1JyBoZWlnaHQ9JzUnIGZpbGw9J3doaXRlJy8+CiAgPHBhdGggZD0nTTAgNUw1IDBaTTYgNEw0IDZaTS0xIDFMMSAtMVonIHN0cm9rZT0nIzg4OCcgc3Ryb2tlLXdpZHRoPScxJy8+Cjwvc3ZnPg=="); 
    background-repeat: repeat;
    position: absolute;
    top: 0px;
    right: 0px;
    bottom: 0px;
    left: 0px;

    border-radius:15%;
}

.g-sector{
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
   
    transform-origin: 0 0;
}
.g-sector-high {
    background: var(--sec-high-color);
    transform: rotate(328deg) skew(12deg, 23deg);

.g-sector-normal {
    background:var(--sec-normal-color);

    left: 0;
    top: 49%;
    width: 100%;
    height: 2%;
    filter:drop-shadow(0px 1px 3px #ff000080);

}
.g-needle-ring {
    position: absolute;
    width: calc(var(--container-size) * 1.5%);

.g-label{
    position: absolute;
    text-align: center;
    left: 50%;
    top: 58%;
    width: 100%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    font-family: monospace;
    font-size:  calc(var(--container-size) * 18%);
    color: #000000a1;
    filter: drop-shadow(2px 3px 2px #00000080);
}
.g-label::after{
    content: var(--g-unit);
    font-size: clamp(1em,calc(var(--container-size) * 40%),1.5em);
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 100%;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
}
.g-rivets{
    position: absolute;
    left:0;
    top:0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
}

.g-rivet {
    position: absolute;
    width: calc(var(--container-size) * 2px);
    height: calc(var(--container-size) * 2px);
    border-radius: 50px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #adadad 0%,#d3d3d3 51%,#d1d1d1 68%,#8c8c8c 100%);
    box-shadow: 0px 2px 4px #000, -1px -1px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
}
.g-rivet:nth-child(1){
    top:calc(var(--container-size) * 1.5px);
    left:calc(var(--container-size) * 1.5px);
}
.g-rivet:nth-child(2){
    top:calc(var(--container-size) * 1.5px);
    right:calc(var(--container-size) * 1.5px);
}
.g-rivet:nth-child(3){
    bottom:calc(var(--container-size) * 1.5px);
    left:calc(var(--container-size) * 1.5px);
}
.g-rivet:nth-child(4){
    bottom:calc(var(--container-size) * 1.5px);
    right:calc(var(--container-size) * 1.5px);
}

.g-rivet::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    top: 50%;
    width: calc(var(--container-size) * 10%);
    height: calc(var(--container-size) * 10%);
    box-shadow: inset 0px 1px 2px #222;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    border-radius: 50%;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
}
</style>

Clock Toolbar
format:
<script id="titleScript" type="text/javascript">

$(function() {
    if($('.md-toolbar-tools').length != 0){
        loadClock();
    }else setTimeout(loadClock, 500)
});

function loadClock(){
    $('#clock').remove();
    var toolbar = $('.md-toolbar-tools');
    
    var div = $('<div/>');
    var p = $('<p/ id="clock">');
    
    div.append(p);
    div[0].style.margin = '5px 5px 5px auto';
    toolbar.append(div);

    function displayTitle(lh) {
        p.text(lh); 
    }
    
    function upTime() {
        var d = new Date();
        p.text(d.toLocaleString('en-IN'));
    }

    if(document.clockInterval){ 
            clearInterval(document.clockInterval);
            document.clockInterval = null;
    }
        
    document.clockInterval = setInterval(upTime,1000);
}

</script>
